Project Title:
Movie Genre Rating Analysis using Hadoop MapReduce

Description:
This project analyzes movie ratings by genre using Hadoop MapReduce and Distributed Cache.

Input Files:
1. movies.txt
2. ratings_1gb.txt

Output:
genre    ratingCount    avgRating    fiveStarCount

Implemented Classes:
- CacheMapper.java
- CacheReducer.java
- CacheDriver.java

Features:
- Distributed Cache
- HashMap lookup
- Data validation
- Hadoop counters
- 1GB dataset processing

Execution Command:
hadoop jar task5.jar CacheDriver \
/user/hadoop/Project_BigData_task5/ratings_1gb.txt \
/user/hadoop/Project_BigData_task5/output_task5_no_combiner \
/user/hadoop/Project_BigData_task5/movies.txt
